Package: wcGeneSummary
Type: Package
Title: Make word cloud from gene set
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Noriaki", "Sato", email = "nori5030@kuhp.kyoto-u.ac.jp", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: This package makes word cloud of gene set using R libraries GeneSummary, tm and wordcloud. Input is gene list. Useful when GSEA or ORA returned no significant results.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
